[Sep 22]                                                                
Alumni                5:0  San Isidro           [at Ferro Carril Oeste (BUE)]
   [J. A. Brown 21, 31, 72, Eliseo Brown 26, Alfredo Brown 27]                          
Belgrano Athletic     0:2  Porteño                   
Quilmes              wp:lp Reformer             [Reformer withdrew]
San Martín Athletic   2:3  Atlético Estudiantes           

Alumni won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:                                  

Alumni:                 T. Duncan; Juan Domingo Brown, Jorge Gibson Brown; 
                     Guillermo R. Ross, Carlos A. Lett, Ernesto Alejandro Brown;
                     Gottlob Eduardo Weiss, Alfredo Carrow Brown, Juan A. Brown, 
                     Eliseo Brown, J. Henry Lawrie.
                                            
San Isidro:          Carlos T. Wilson; J. S. Valle, Santiago Pío Gallino; J. A. 
                     Goodfellow, H. O. Goodfellow, Luis M. Vernet Amadeo; Lucio 
                     Burgos, W. J. Jones, Juan Olegario Gil, Juan S. Rossi, 
                     Ricardo S. Malbrán.
                                                
Referee:             W. J. Williams.                                    
                                                                                
